{"Body": "On Monday, September 3, 2012, Highland Village Police Officer Luis Flores was found deceased at his Carrollton residence. Officer Flores had been with the Highland Village Police Department since November 2008 and was a member of the HVPD Bike Unit. He received the Life Saving Award in December 2009 and was awarded an HVPD Certificate of Merit. He was 30 years old.\n\n \n\n \"It is with a very heavy heart that we report the loss of one of our family members. Luis Flores was an officer of character and integrity, he will be sorely missed. Our prayers are with his family,\" said City Manager Michael Leavitt.", "Title": "Luis Stephen Flores"}